doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Aksolabs - Innovation through agility

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Catamaran:100,200,300,400,500,600,700,800,900' rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,100i,300,300i,400,400i,700,700i,900,900i' rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Header
        header.masthead.img-bg.text-center.text-white
            .masthead-content
                .container.px-5
                    h1.masthead-heading.mb-0 Aksolabs Limited
                    h2.masthead-subheading.mb-0 Software delivery, consultancy, coaching and enablement
                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.rounded-pill.mt-5(href='#scroll') Learn More

        // Content section 1
        section#scroll
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/whatWeDo.jpg', alt='What we do')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 What we do
                            p
                                | At Aksolabs, we understand that making great software can be hard. We also understand that with the right team, making great software can be a breeze. That's why our experts are on hand to help craft solutions that help you get back to focusing on growing your business.
                            p
                                | With over a decade's experience of crafting solutions in our lab, we are well positioned to assist businesses in myriad sectors and of various sizes.
                            p
                                | So if you are in need of great solutions that solve your problems while also being scalable and maintainable, #[a(href='#getInTouch') get in touch] to see how we can help turbo charge your business.

        // Content section 2
        section
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/howWeDoIt.jpg', alt='How we do it')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 How we do it
                            p
                                | Teamwork, collaboration and effective communication are essential to achieve the greatest results.
                            p
                                | We use Agile and Lean methods to deliver useful software into production sooner. 
                            p
                                | We automate processes to increase quality and reliability of said software.
                            p
                                | We leverage the very best cloud services so you don't have to think about infrastructure.
                            p
                                | We monitor and alert to provide maximum visibility to end users.
                            p
                                | We use the right technology that will keep your solutions serving your business for longer. 
                            
        // Content section 3
        section#getInTouch
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/contactUs.jpg', alt='Contact Us')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Get in touch
                            p 
                                | Please fill in the #[a(href='#contactUs') form below] if you would like to get in touch
                            p
                                | You can also find us on #[a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/company/82009710/') LinkedIn]
        
        // Content section 4
        section#contactUs
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/aksolabsLogo.jpg', alt='How we do it')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Send us a message!
                            form(action="https://formspree.io/f/xeqneyla" method="POST" id="my-form")
                                div(class="mb-3")
                                    label(class="form-label" for="emailInput") Email:
                                    input(class="form-control" type="email" name="email" id="emailInput")
                                div(class="mb-3")
                                    label(class="form-label" for="messageInput") Message:
                                    textarea(class="form-control" name="message" id="messageInput")
                                div(class="mb-3")
                                    button(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="my-form-button") Submit
                            p#my-form-status
                                
        // Footer
        footer.py-5.bg-black
            .container.px-5
                p.m-0.text-center.text-white.small Copyright &copy; Aksolabs Limited 2022

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
